    "description": {
      "es": "",
      "en": "Creates a temporary directory in the most secure manner possible. There are no race conditions in the directory’s creation. The directory is readable, writable, and searchable only by the creating user ID. The user of mkdtemp() is responsible for deleting the temporary directory and its contents when done with it. The prefix, suffix, and dir arguments are the same as for mkstemp(). mkdtemp() returns the absolute pathname of the new directory. Raises an auditing event tempfile.mkdtemp with arg..."
